<div class='section-title'><h2><%= I18n.t('about') %></h2></div>

<section>

  <% if I18n.locale.to_s == 'ja' %>
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      日本生活の「初心者」と「ベテラン」を繋ぎ、<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      多様性に富んだ美しく多彩な日本を築くためのコミュニティーサイトです。</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      日本の文化が世界で称賛され、海外から日本へ訪れる人々が増えました。<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      良い影響もたくさんある一方で、様々な問題も生じます。</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      来日なさった人々にとっては、リスペクトを持って日本へ訪れたにもかかわらず、<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      初めての文化や常識に戸惑い、上手く順応できない場面があります。<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      一方で、日本に元々住んでいる人々にとっては、<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      生活に根付いてきた大切にしたい文化や常識を脅かされることに<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      不安を覚える場面に遭遇することがあります。</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-5'>
      全員が互いを理解し合うための手助けがしたいという想いから、<span class='responsive-disabled'></br></span>
      日本生活の「初心者」と「ベテラン」の間での相互理解を促すために当サイトを制作いたしました。
    </p>
    
  <% else %>
    
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      This website is to make connections between beginners and veterans in life in Japan
      and to make future Japan variegated and beautiful for everyone.</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      Fortunately, to experience Japanese culture is admired in the world and a lot of people have been visiting Japan.
      That give Japan a positive impact. Whereas some problems happen at the same time.</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      Some of first-time visitors, who have a lot of respect for Japanese cultures and people, 
      sometimes get confused by common senses and cultures in a new place and feel difficulty in adapting.</p>
    
    <p class='text-center mb-3'>
      On the other hand, some of people who have roots in Japan feel anxious about cultures and common senses 
      they have been cherishing are threatened.</p>
  
    <p class='text-center mb-5'>
      Therefore, a desire to help them understand each other brought me 
      to create this website which promotes mutual understanding between "beginners" and "veterans" in life in Japan.</p>
    
  <% end %>

</section>
